OL,3,CGirl from Gaza's wish for peace as she
OL,4,Cplays with her teddies to pretend the
OL,5,Cwar is over
OL,7,FAs children around the world write
OL,8,Fletters filled with Christmas wishes
OL,9,Fto Santa, Jana Jibril Abu Taima, from
OL,10,FGaza, has just one wish - to enter the
OL,11,Fnew year in safety.
OL,13,FLike most 11 year-olds Jana and her
OL,14,Ffriends' days are filled with games
OL,15,Fand stories of make believe.
OL,17,FBut over two months into a conflict
OL,18,Fwhich has claimed the lives of nearly
OL,19,F20,000 Palestinians, even their
OL,20,Fimaginations cannot escape this war.
